t, which will allow you to sell your products with an unlimited number of combinations and to show users the price change in real time.\n	</div>\n		<div class="cols col-sm-3 ">\n			<div class="general-features">\n\n		<div class="quick-info">\n\n\n			<h3>Quick info</h3>\n\n			<ul class="list-unstyled info">\n\n				<li>\n					Requires:<span><b>WordPress 4.0 or higher</b></span>\n				</li>\n\n				<li>\n					Compatible up to:<span><b>WordPress 4.5</b></span>\n				</li>\n\n									<li>\n						Requires:<span><b>WooCommerce 2.5.0 or higher</b></span>\n					</li>\n				\n									<li>\n						Compatible up to:<span><b>WooCommerce 2.5.x</b></span>\n					</li>\n				\n									<li>\n						Minimum PHP version:<span><b>5.4</b></span>\n					</li>\n				\n				<li>\n					<span class="version">version						<b>1.0.6</b> - released						<b>2016-04-14</b></span>\n				</li>\n\n				\n\n			</ul>\n\n\n			<a class="btn-sm btn-flat-green" href="https://yithemes.com/docs-plugins/yith-woocommerce-advanced-product-options/"\n			   title="View documentation"\n			   target="_blank">View documentation</a>\n			<a class="btn-sm btn-flat-green" href="#" title="View changelog"\n			   data-toggle="modal" data-target="#changelog">View changelog</a>\n		</div>\n\n		<div class="modal fade" id="changelog" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="changelogLabel"\n		     aria-hidden="true">\n			<div class="modal-dialog">\n				<div class="modal-content">\n					<div class="modal-body">\n						<button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span\n								aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>\n						\n		\n		<h4>Version 1.0.6 - Released: Apr 14, 2016</h4>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Fixed: Prevent notice on products loop</li>\n            </ul>\n		<h4>Version 1.0.5 - Released: Apr 13, 2016</h4>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Added: WordPress 4.5 support</li>\n            </ul>\n		<h4>Version 1.0.4 - Released: Apr 12, 2016</h4>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Fixed: Request a quote button not working in the products loop</li>\n                <li>Fixed: Removed unuseless query execution</li>\n            </ul>\n		<h4>Version 1.0.3 - Released: Apr 09, 2016</h4>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Added: WPML support</li>\n				<li>Fixed: Options total price was not correct when user change quantity on single product page</li>\n            </ul>\n		<h4>Version 1.0.2 - Released: Apr 04, 2016</h4>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Fixed: Options are not saved when a quote was inserted inside a label</li>\n            </ul>\n		<h4>Version 1.0.1 - Released: Apr 01, 2016</h4>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Fixed: Price total doesn'' t change after option is selected on quick view</li>\n            </ul>\n		<h4>Version 1.0.0 - Released: Mar 31, 2016</h4>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Initial Release</li>\n            </ul>\n		\n    					</div>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n\n\n	</div>\n		</div>\n		</div>\n	\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">WITH <span class="green">THIS PLUGIN</span> YOU CAN:</h2>\n	<div class="row border">\n		\n	<div class="cols col-sm-6 ">\n		\n	<div class="image_title">\n					<h2>\n				Create groups of options			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				And choose to use them for all products of the shop, only for specific categories or limited on a single product			</h3>\n			<div class="image_title_content">\n							</div>\n			</div>\n\n		<div class="image-from-id">\n	<img width="600" height="826" src="https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/01-10.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full" alt="Create options group" srcset="https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/01-10-218x300.jpg 218w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/01-10-382x526.jpg 382w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/01-10.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" />	</div>\n		</div>\n		<div class="cols col-sm-6 border">\n		\n	<div class="image_title">\n					<h2>\n				Choose from different options			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				Checkbox, color, date, label list, number, select, radio button, text, textarea, upload			</h3>\n			<div class="image_title_content">\n							</div>\n			</div>\n\n		<div class="image-from-id">\n	<img width="600" height="1075" src="https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/02-8.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full" alt="Advanced options" srcset="https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/02-8-572x1024.jpg 572w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/02-8-382x684.jpg 382w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/02-8.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" />	</div>\n		</div>\n	\n	</div>\n	\n\n	<div class="row border">\n		\n	<div class="cols col-sm-6 ">\n		\n	<div class="image_title">\n					<h2>\n				Set dependency between the options			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				To show a dropdown option only to users who selected\nthe one that depends on it			</h3>\n			<div class="image_title_content">\n							</div>\n			</div>\n\n		<div class="image-from-id">\n	<img width="600" height="643" src="https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/03-5.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full" alt="Requirement options" srcset="https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/03-5-280x300.jpg 280w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/03-5-382x409.jpg 382w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/03-5-128x137.jpg 128w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/03-5.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" />	</div>\n		</div>\n		<div class="cols col-sm-6 border">\n		\n	<div class="image_title">\n					<h2>\n				Increase the cost of product			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				By assigning a fixed or percentage price to any of the options selected by user			</h3>\n			<div class="image_title_content">\n							</div>\n			</div>\n\n		<div class="image-from-id">\n	<img width="600" height="643" src="https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/04-4.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full" alt="P