d in pending status.\nYou would make every effort to see it as completed, whereas the only thing you can do is to wait for users decision and if he/she wont complete that order, it will be removed from system. As a consequence, you will lose both the sale and the customer.";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"Samantha P.";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:8062:"	<div class="row ">\n			<div class="cols col-sm-9 ">\n		\n<h3>It would be wonderful to understand why those orders acquire a pending status, wouldnt it?</h3>\nOur <strong>Pending Survey</strong> has been studied with this purpose!\nOnce installed and configured, you could send an automatic email to users with a pending order, which allows you to establish a relationship with them and, possibly, to ask them if they have found issues during the purchase or the reason why they didnt complete that order.\nYou could also stimulate users to give an answer by offering them a discount coupon. In this way you will obtain:\n<ul>\n	<li>the answers you need to fix potential obstacles on your e-commerce and to optimize your sales;</li>\n	<li>a radical decreased percentage of pending orders;</li>\n	<li>&#8230;and your customers loyalty!</li>\n</ul>\n	</div>\n		<div class="cols col-sm-3 ">\n			<div class="general-features">\n\n		<div class="quick-info">\n\n\n			<h3>Quick info</h3>\n\n			<ul class="list-unstyled info">\n\n				<li>\n					Requires:<span><b>WordPress 4.0 or higher</b></span>\n				</li>\n\n				<li>\n					Compatible up to:<span><b>WordPress 4.4.x</b></span>\n				</li>\n\n									<li>\n						Requires:<span><b>WooCommerce 2.4.0 or higher</b></span>\n					</li>\n				\n									<li>\n						Compatible up to:<span><b>WooCommerce 2.5.x</b></span>\n					</li>\n				\n									<li>\n						Minimum PHP version:<span><b>5.4</b></span>\n					</li>\n				\n				<li>\n					<span class="version">version						<b>1.0.0</b> - released						<b>2016-02-11</b></span>\n				</li>\n\n				\n\n			</ul>\n\n\n			<a class="btn-sm btn-flat-green" href="https://yithemes.com/docs-plugins/yith-woocommerce-pending-order-survey/"\n			   title="View documentation"\n			   target="_blank">View documentation</a>\n			<a class="btn-sm btn-flat-green" href="#" title="View changelog"\n			   data-toggle="modal" data-target="#changelog">View changelog</a>\n		</div>\n\n		<div class="modal fade" id="changelog" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="changelogLabel"\n		     aria-hidden="true">\n			<div class="modal-dialog">\n				<div class="modal-content">\n					<div class="modal-body">\n						<button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span\n								aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>\n						\n\n<h4>Version 1.0.0 - Released: Feb 11, 2016 </h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Initial Release</li>\n</ul>\n\n    					</div>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n\n\n	</div>\n		</div>\n		</div>\n	\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">WITH <span class="green">THIS PLUGIN</span> YOU CAN:</h2>\n\n	<div class="row border">\n		\n	<div class="cols col-sm-6 ">\n		\n	<div class="image_title">\n					<h2>\n				Create one or more surveys			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				to share with users which orders are still pending			</h3>\n			<div class="image_title_content">\n							</div>\n			</div>\n\n		<div class="image-from-id">\n	<img width="600" height="857" src="https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/015.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full" alt="Multiple surveys" srcset="https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/015-210x300.jpg 210w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/015-382x546.jpg 382w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/015-96x137.jpg 96w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/015.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" />	</div>\n		</div>\n		<div class="cols col-sm-6 border">\n		\n	<div class="image_title">\n					<h2>\n				Send a thank-you email when the order is completed			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				to every user who has answered the survey			</h3>\n			<div class="image_title_content">\n							</div>\n			</div>\n\n		<div class="image-from-id">\n	<img width="600" height="857" src="https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/025.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full" alt="Thankyou email" srcset="https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/025-210x300.jpg 210w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/025-382x546.jpg 382w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/025-96x137.jpg 96w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/025.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" />	</div>\n		</div>\n	\n	</div>\n	\n\n	<div class="row border">\n		\n	<div class="cols col-sm-6 ">\n		\n	<div class="image_title">\n					<h2>\n				Offer a discount on your products			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				by adding a coupon code in the survey email			</h3>\n			<div class="image_title_content">\n							</div>\n			</div>\n\n		<div class="image-from-id">\n	<img width="600" height="767" src="https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/035.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full" alt="Coupon settings" srcset="https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/035-235x300.jpg 235w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/035-382x488.jpg 382w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/035.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" />	</div>\n		</div>\n		<div class="cols col-sm-6 border">\n		\n	<div class="image_title">\n					<h2>\n				Recover pending orders			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				and invite users to retry purchasing through the link you can provide in the survey email			</h3>\n			<div class="image_title_content">\n							</div>\n			</div>\n\n		<div class="image-from-id">\n	<img width="600" height="767