rveys in the &#8220;Checkout&#8221; page. Furthermore, through the statistics, you can obtain information that will be precious for your future choices.\n\nStop losing money and trust your customers!\n	</div>\n		<div class="cols col-sm-3 ">\n			<div class="general-features">\n\n		<div class="quick-info">\n\n\n			<h3>Quick info</h3>\n\n			<ul class="list-unstyled info">\n\n				<li>\n					Requires:<span><b>WordPress 4.0 or higher</b></span>\n				</li>\n\n				<li>\n					Compatible up to:<span><b>WordPress 4.4.x</b></span>\n				</li>\n\n									<li>\n						Requires:<span><b>WooCommerce 2.4.0 or higher</b></span>\n					</li>\n				\n									<li>\n						Compatible up to:<span><b>WooCommerce 2.5.x</b></span>\n					</li>\n				\n									<li>\n						Minimum PHP version:<span><b>5.4</b></span>\n					</li>\n				\n				<li>\n					<span class="version">version						<b>1.0.4</b> - released						<b>2016-01-21</b></span>\n				</li>\n\n				\n\n			</ul>\n\n\n			<a class="btn-sm btn-flat-green" href="https://yithemes.com/docs-plugins/yith-woocommerce-surveys/"\n			   title="View documentation"\n			   target="_blank">View documentation</a>\n			<a class="btn-sm btn-flat-green" href="#" title="View changelog"\n			   data-toggle="modal" data-target="#changelog">View changelog</a>\n		</div>\n\n		<div class="modal fade" id="changelog" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="changelogLabel"\n		     aria-hidden="true">\n			<div class="modal-dialog">\n				<div class="modal-content">\n					<div class="modal-body">\n						<button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span\n								aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>\n						\n		\n		<h4>Version 1.0.4 - Released on Jan 21, 2015</h4>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Added: Option to sort Surveys by date or by name</li>\n                <li>Update: Language File</li>\n                <li>Fixed: input text field "disabled" on Firefox</li>\n            </ul>\n		<h4>Version 1.0.3 - Released on Dec 15, 2015</h4>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Added: Compatibility with YIT WooCommerce Product Slider Carousel</li>\n                <li>Fixed: Warning array_merge(), Argument #2 is not an array</li>\n            </ul>\n		 <h4>Version 1.0.2 - Released on Dec 14, 2015</h4>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Fix show only 5 answer in admin</li>\n                <li>Updated Plugin Framework</li>\n            </ul>\n		<h4>Version 1.0.1 - Released on Dec 05, 2015 </h4>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Initial Release</li>\n            </ul>\n		\n    					</div>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n\n\n	</div>\n		</div>\n		</div>\n	\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">WITH THE <span class="green">PREMIUM VERSION</span> OF THIS PLUGINYOU CAN:</h2>\n\n	<div class="row border">\n		\n	<div class="cols col-sm-6 ">\n		\n	<div class="image_title">\n					<h2>\n				CREATE ALL THE SURVEYS YOU WANT			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				And allow unlimited answers from the users			</h3>\n			<div class="image_title_content">\n							</div>\n			</div>\n\n		<div class="image-from-id">\n	<img width="600" height="820" src="https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/01.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full" alt="Infinite questions and answers" srcset="https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/01-382x522.jpg 382w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/01.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" />	</div>\n		</div>\n		<div class="cols col-sm-6 border">\n		\n	<div class="image_title">\n					<h2>\n				TAKE ADVANTAGE OF THE ``CHECKOUT`` PAGE			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				Include the question in the Checkout page and choose the best position			</h3>\n			<div class="image_title_content">\n							</div>\n			</div>\n\n		<div class="image-from-id">\n	<img width="600" height="820" src="https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/02.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full" alt="Survey in checkout page" srcset="https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/02-382x522.jpg 382w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/02.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" />	</div>\n		</div>\n	\n	</div>\n	\n\n	<div class="row border">\n		\n	<div class="cols col-sm-6 ">\n		\n	<div class="image_title">\n					<h2>\n				INCLUDE A MANDATORY SURVEY			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				And force the users to answer to complete their order			</h3>\n			<div class="image_title_content">\n							</div>\n			</div>\n\n		<div class="image-from-id">\n	<img width="600" height="735" src="https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/03.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full" alt="Mandatory answer" srcset="https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/03-245x300.jpg 245w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/03-382x468.jpg 382w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/03-112x137.jpg 112w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/03.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" />	</div>\n		</div>\n		<div class="cols col-sm-6 border">\n		\n	<div class="image_title">\n					<h2>\n				INCLUDE THE SURVEYS IN THE PRODUCT DETAIL PAGE			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				And choose to apply the question to one or more products			</h3>\n			<div class="image_title_content">\n							</div>\n			</div>\n\n		<div class="image-from-id">\n	<img width="600" height="735" src="https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/04.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full" alt="Widget and shortcode" srcset="https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/04-245x300.jpg 245w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/04-382x468.jpg 382w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/04-112x137.jpg 112w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/04.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" />	</div>\n		</div>\n	\n	</div>\n	\n\n	<div class="row border">\n		\n	<div class="cols col-sm-6 ">\n		\n	<div class="image_title">\n					<h2>\n				CREATE THE SURVEY IN ANY PAGE			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				By widget or shortcode and customize the pages creat