eposit and Down Payments</strong> can turn out to be an ace up your sleeve for you shop, especially if you sell middle- or high-cost products: certainly, the higher the price of your products the easier you can lose customers because they cannot pay immediately the total amount. More than a reliable plugin, a guarantee: let your customers leave a deposit and, besides loyalise them, you&#8217;ll see your shop conversion rate increase.\n	</div>\n		<div class="cols col-sm-3 ">\n			<div class="general-features">\n\n		<div class="quick-info">\n\n\n			<h3>Quick info</h3>\n\n			<ul class="list-unstyled info">\n\n				<li>\n					Requires:<span><b>WordPress 4.0 or higher</b></span>\n				</li>\n\n				<li>\n					Compatible up to:<span><b>WordPress 4.5</b></span>\n				</li>\n\n									<li>\n						Requires:<span><b>WooCommerce 2.4.0 or higher</b></span>\n					</li>\n				\n									<li>\n						Compatible up to:<span><b>WooCommerce 2.5.x</b></span>\n					</li>\n				\n									<li>\n						Minimum PHP version:<span><b>5.4</b></span>\n					</li>\n				\n				<li>\n					<span class="version">version						<b>1.0.1</b> - released						<b>2015-12-01</b></span>\n				</li>\n\n				\n\n			</ul>\n\n\n			<a class="btn-sm btn-flat-green" href="https://yithemes.com/docs-plugins/yith-woocommerce-deposits-and-down-payments/"\n			   title="View documentation"\n			   target="_blank">View documentation</a>\n			<a class="btn-sm btn-flat-green" href="#" title="View changelog"\n			   data-toggle="modal" data-target="#changelog">View changelog</a>\n		</div>\n\n		<div class="modal fade" id="changelog" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="changelogLabel"\n		     aria-hidden="true">\n			<div class="modal-dialog">\n				<div class="modal-content">\n					<div class="modal-body">\n						<button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span\n								aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>\n						\n		\n		<h4>Version 1.0.1 - Released on Dec 01, 2015 </h4>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Initial Release</li>\n            </ul>\n		\n    					</div>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n\n\n	</div>\n		</div>\n		</div>\n	\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">WITH THE <span class="green">PREMIUM VERSION</span> OF THIS PLUGINYOU CAN:</h2>\n\n	<div class="row border">\n		\n	<div class="cols col-sm-6 ">\n		\n	<div class="image_title">\n					<h2>\n				Set a fixed amount for the deposit			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				or let the plugin calculate as a percent value of product price			</h3>\n			<div class="image_title_content">\n							</div>\n			</div>\n\n		<div class="image-from-id">\n	<img width="600" height="647" src="https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/017.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full" alt="Deposit amount" srcset="https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/017-278x300.jpg 278w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/017-382x412.jpg 382w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/017-127x137.jpg 127w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/017.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" />	</div>\n		</div>\n		<div class="cols col-sm-6 border">\n		\n	<div class="image_title">\n					<h2>\n				Choose until when the deposit is valid			</h2>\n		\n					<h3>\n				and make it expire if the balance is not paid in time			</h3>\n			<div class="image_title_content">\n							</div>\n			</div>\n\n		<div class="image-from-id">\n	<img width="600" height="647" src="https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/025.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full" alt="Expiration" srcset="https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/025-278x300.jpg 278w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/025-382x412.jpg 382w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/025-127x137.jpg 127w, https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/025.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" />	</div>\n		</div>\n	\n	</div>\n	\n\n	<div class="row border">\n		\n	<div class="cols col-sm-6 ">\n		\n	<div class="image_title">